{"tid":1980431,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"基建狂魔中共最新作品 - 世界最長跨的海峽高鐵大橋！坐高鐵過大海！將來或可坐高鐵直達台北！","createTime":"2020-04-20T05:51:19.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-30T06:56:41.000Z","uid":109923,"like":1,"dislike":29,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"ddb3168f197833c35c75e9064c0b943b4e0c777f","tid":1980431,"uid":109923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T05:51:19.000Z","msg":"大橋的福州至平潭鐵路是合福高鐵的重要延伸，對構建北京至福州、平潭高鐵，完善區域綜合交通網絡，助推海峽兩岸經貿合作、文化交流和人員往來起到重要作用。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/u45xfcd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fu45xfcd.jpg&h=d96f7bfc&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n大橋所在的平潭海峽為世界三大風口海域之一，具有風大、浪高、水深、流急等特點。據統計，每年6級以上大風超過300天，7級以上大風超過200天，最大浪高約9.69米，波浪力是長江等內河的10倍以上，曾被稱為&ldquo;建橋禁區&rdquo;。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0rJnCqv.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0rJnCqv.gif&h=6d8ea966&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nw1TJ5w.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fnw1TJ5w.gif&h=b0edcb55&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n近日，央視專門報導了平潭海峽大橋的建設進展，透露鐵路軌道鋪設工作將於5月底完成，隨後進入項目驗收階段，預計11月底開通運行。到時候，就可以開車、坐高鐵過大海了！<br />\n<br />\n同時，國鐵集團還公佈了一組衛星圖，可以能清楚地看到這座超級橋樑從無到有的歷程。<br />\n<br />\n據悉，平潭海峽公鐵大橋全長16.34公里，起於福建省長樂市，經人嶼島、長嶼島、小練島、大練島，從蘇澳鎮上平潭島，包括跨越元洪航道、鼓嶼門水道、大小練島水道的三座航道橋，均為鋼桁結合梁斜拉橋。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fU991Sc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfU991Sc.jpg&h=7d29bec4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pPLM35y.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpPLM35y.jpg&h=ca93a868&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n大橋為鐵路公路兩用，上層是設計時速為100公里的6車道高速公路，下層是設計時速為200公里的雙線I級鐵路。<br />\n<br />\n全橋共計228個橋墩，鋼結構用量124萬噸，混凝土用量294萬方，均是迄今為止國內外橋樑之最，可滿足海上橋面在十級大風環境下安全運營。"},{"pid":"b9fb89e06cf1766d47a677d14daa2b146479993c","tid":1980431,"uid":7369,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T05:54:51.000Z","msg":"聽講台灣會地震喎"},{"pid":"731eaa610592494e1935aa40fdeb06e4a846eff7","tid":1980431,"uid":289946,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T05:55:32.000Z","msg":"Gdp gogogoo"},{"pid":"b0a160caac1a3064b47dc433f5764aa80d6fa98e","tid":1980431,"uid":196924,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T05:56:48.000Z","msg":"條橋本身100<br />\n但係大風少少都50<br />\n好似港豬澳咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"38dce6bf66ad899d72b1d42695d8d581b99b9ceb","tid":1980431,"uid":31215,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T05:59:40.000Z","msg":"厲害了 nmsl國"},{"pid":"c028c0a8a3fd3d5a3ec877eb8b24d869736773e6","tid":1980431,"uid":145868,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T06:18:48.000Z","msg":"一個颱風打埋去，條橋除時收皮"},{"pid":"0fd1193ed7058b6c2a957595e887be3dd87661d3","tid":1980431,"uid":26424,"like":2,"dislike":18,"score":-16,"quote":{"pid":"c028c0a8a3fd3d5a3ec877eb8b24d869736773e6","tid":1980431,"uid":145868,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T06:18:48.000Z","msg":"一個颱風打埋去，條橋除時收皮"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T06:23:53.000Z","msg":"港珠澳收皮未？福建有成個台灣擋風"},{"pid":"c15fde84f7299444c629de603df9563c96253d44","tid":1980431,"uid":4672,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T06:25:20.000Z","msg":"成碟青瓜過大海"},{"pid":"71960b16c4dd628a0282b69c058fb7854026c209","tid":1980431,"uid":145868,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"0fd1193ed7058b6c2a957595e887be3dd87661d3","tid":1980431,"uid":26424,"like":2,"dislike":18,"score":-16,"quote":{"pid":"c028c0a8a3fd3d5a3ec877eb8b24d869736773e6","tid":1980431,"uid":145868,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T06:18:48.000Z","msg":"一個颱風打埋去，條橋除時收皮"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T06:23:53.000Z","msg":"港珠澳收皮未？福建有成個台灣擋風"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T06:32:58.000Z","msg":"有冇睇內容？地理位置講到明唔適宜起橋，有天災真係除時收皮"},{"pid":"6f5e848f1cfad692657f27480cd98279a6bff0